1. Brajane *su* vrsta kruške koja se najčešće koristi za spravljanje kompota. (*Brajane* are a type of pear that is most commonly used for making compote.) 
2. Kupila sam kilogram *brajana* na pijaci. (I bought a kilogram of *brajana* at the market.) 
3. U mom dvorištu rastu *brajane* jabuke. (*Brajane* apples are growing in my yard.) 
4. Za večeru smo imali *brajani* pasulj. (We had *brajani* bean stew for dinner.) 
5. Mlinar je mleo *brajano* brašno. (The miller ground *brajano* flour.) 
6. U školi učimo da pišemo na *brajanoj* ploči. (In school, we learn to write on a *brajana* board.) 
7. Proizvođači tvrde da *brajana* olovka traje mnogo duže od obične. (Manufacturers claim that *brajana* pencil lasts much longer than a regular one.) 
8. Sela su povezana *brajanom* putnom mrežom. (The villages are connected by a *brajana* road network.) 
9. *Brajane* knjige se koriste za štampanje brailovog pisma. (*Brajana* books are used for printing braille.) 
10. *Brajanim* pismom je lako pisati na papiru sa ispupčenim slovima. (It is easy to write on paper with raised letters using *brajana* script.)